{"tid":1632301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"是否由香港政府所策劃的恐怖襲擊 ?? 的士撞入示威人群謀殺示威民眾及激起對立","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:06:19.000Z","uid":229436,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e182b7835e42f53ae17a03e6b0df1feb577830","tid":1632301,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3C4qiMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3C4qiMN.jpg&h=94f5b3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府所策劃的恐怖襲擊 ?? </span></span><br />\n的士司機是否收取政府金錢 <br />\n故意撞入示威人群謀殺反政府蒙面法的示威民眾及激起對立<br />\n借市民殺市民 買兇殺人?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以近月警方幾近謀殺的行為推斷<br />\n有無可能香港政府除左利用香港警察部隊殺人外<br />\n更會動用更多支持政府的恐怖份子 以謀殺示威者為目標<br />\n再次恐襲所有普通市民/示威者? <br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JzA2y-wSOvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJzA2y-wSOvs&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=e7ea7c4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JzA2y-wSOvs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人政權 香港人何去何從???</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ea3d850b22926def9236b8273df78b224980c19","tid":1632301,"uid":15259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:33:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"169d21007411e3f35f45b849a7d21161ac939f4a","tid":1632301,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:08.000Z","msg":"政府到底要我地香港人何去何從<br />\n5大訴求缺一不可已經講左4個月<br />\n警察濫權濫暴已經4個月<br />\n一次又一次傷害 殺害 抹黑香港市民<br />\n到底香港政府要將我地香港市民屠殺到一個什麼地步"},{"pid":"df168e0b44129723bd6fdfb221f05f9270e